text: Ragne Tangen (12 March 1927 - 9 May 2015) was a Norwegian children's television presenter. Her career began in 1958. She then made the first children's television program in Norway, I kosekroken. Tangen died on 9 May 2015 at the age of 88. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Norwegian actors Category:Norwegian television personalities
